snippet.title: BEST BEAUTY PRODUCTS 2018 | AMBER HOWE
snippet.description:
Hey Beauties! Here is my last best beauty video for 2018. This one is all my favourites haircare and bath/body products from 2018. This was a hard one to narrow down hence why it took me a little longer to film but here it is my best beauty products of 2018. 

PRODUCTS MENTIONED:

MAUI MOISTURE SHAMPOO AND CONDITONER:
https://www.boots.com/search/MAUI+MOISTURE

OGX SHAMPOO AND CONDITIONER:
https://www.boots.com/search/OGX

HASK HAIR MASK:
https://www.superdrug.com/Hair/Hair-Treatments/Conditioning-Treatments/HASK-Keratin-Protein-Smoothing-Deep-Conditioner-50ml/p/609901

BATISTE DRY SHAMPOO:

https://www.boots.com/batiste/batiste-stylist

 HASK HAIR OILS:
https://www.boots.com/hask-argan-oil-from-morocco-repairing-shine-hair-oil-vial-18ml-10193414

https://www.fragrancedirect.co.uk/technic-tan-out-of-ten-tan-lotion-dark-250ml-0086483.html

https://www.boots.com/palmers-cocoa-butter-formula-natural-bronze-gradual-tanning-moisturiser-250ml-10121588

NORVELL SELF TANNER AND CC CREAM:
http://www.norvelltanning.co.uk/shop/product/VENETIAN-SELF-TANNER-CC-CREAM

MITCHUM DEODRANT:
https://www.boots.com/mitchum-advanced-women-pure-fresh-48hr-protection-anti-perspirant-deodorant-200ml

THIS WORKS DEEP SLEEP SPRAY:
https://www.feelunique.com/p/this-works-Deep-Sleep-Pillow-Spray-75ml?gclid=Cj0KCQiAm5viBRD4ARIsADGUT25Jp-uC8FRkdUxVGDYjg1uFD6iKi_6AYXAVKMzxSKtlMdyoaEupsU4aAn7wEALw_wcB&gclsrc=aw.ds

MISSGUIDED BOSS BABE PERFUME:
https://www.missguided.co.uk/boss-babe-eau-de-parfum-80ml-10111084

HUGO BOSS ORANGE FOR HER:
https://www.superdrug.com/Hugo-Boss/BOSS-Orange-Woman-Eau-de-Toilette-75ml/p/564753

VIKTOR AND ROLF BON BON:
https://www.boots.com/viktor-and-rolf-bonbon-eau-de-parfum-50ml-10176818
 
BEING BY SANCTUARY SALTED CARAMEL AND MACADAMIA BODY MIST:
https://www.boots.com/being-by-sanctuary-spa-salted-caramel-and-macadamia-body-mist-10228426

***
I'm Amber and I make videos about all things beauty, fashion and lifestyle related! . I chat about my latest beauty, makeup and fashion finds in my hauls and reviews. I take you along with me from time to time, showing you my daily life in my vlogs!
